Attachments / Documents HR must collect (add to offer packet)
- PAN card copy (mandatory) and bank details for stipend payment.
- Aadhaar or other photo ID.
- Proof of Bengaluru residence (utility bill, rental agreement) if remote Bengaluru residency is required.
- Proof of student status/enrolment (if applicable) or apprenticeship registration (if apprenticeship).
- Signed Background Verification Consent (inserted above).
- Signed Confidentiality + IP Assignment clause (may be included in offer acceptance).
- Signed declaration of other employment/expected annual income (for TDS assessment).

Notes on drafting approach
- Preserve record that this is a training engagement: keep a learning plan and periodic sign‑offs to demonstrate training purpose if classification is challenged.
- If Company intends to treat intern as employee on payroll (for any reason), remove the non‑employee language and ensure statutory registrations and payroll deductions are done. 
